					"type": 23,
					"value": "Group dialog with priestess Yannis and the hollyphant detective.\r\nThe tollyphant tells Yannis that she has solved the crime and leaves afterwards.\r\n!!! It is possible for the player to solve the murder case before this dialog happens, so we need to have a reactivity to it."
